Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.11,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.71,0:00:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.86,0:00:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗噗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.12,0:00:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘恩一行人為了打倒魔龍流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.19,0:00:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而來到了火龍的狩獵場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.17,0:00:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在旁白之後突然停下啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.26,0:00:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就叫猶豫了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.50,0:00:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星究竟是怎樣的龍啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人期待的興奮不已呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.36,0:00:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!快點出來吧!\N我的手在癢了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.64,0:00:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，潘恩真賣力呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.48,0:00:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀，好弱的勇者…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.85,0:00:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的流星!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.98,0:00:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不怕我這\N佛雷姆之王的卡修大人哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.26,0:00:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.76,0:00:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.30,0:00:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.11,0:01:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是龍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛!太可愛了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.61,0:01:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招，流星!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.44,0:01:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓你見識佛雷姆的剽悍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.91,0:01:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢把卡修陛下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.95,0:01:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣哭嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.75,0:01:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺我好像是個大壞人似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!那我就要用魔法將你打倒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.13,0:01:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此這般如此這般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.26,0:01:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回應我的召喚吧\N偉大的風之王，依爾庫啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何，認輸了吧，龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是龍，好強的魔力啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.86,0:01:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
